	   <tr><td colspan=2>Personally I found mend extremely unreliable until about skill level 80. It would frequently worsen at a critical moment in battle, resulting in my death. It will not do any critical failures once it is mastered (skill level 101). Maybe I am just the unluckiest monk in the world, but I have had mend fail with skill 100 :).<br><br>Todoroki<br>Torvonnilous<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
